job_history.work_description: Performed all business responsibilities for the Rehab Department of a Physician group practice. Program development, business growth, and customer service.
Implemented business plans and growth potential through expanding outreach clinics and outpatient facilities.

Performed business duties to increase revenue through higher patient referrals by means of marketing strategies, decreased debt and increased overall profit so company could re-sell clinic for higher profit.
Led the planning and achievement of goals and objectives consistent with the agency mission and philosophy.
Introduced, negotiated and implemented new projects to expand scope of engagement.

skills.name: Business Management
skills.explanation: Over 20 years of experience in various business management roles, including Operations Manager, Healthcare Business Director, Business Director, and Business Manager, indicating expert-level mastery.

skills.name: Leadership
skills.explanation: Consistently held leadership positions, including leading teams and departments, and implementing business plans, showing expert-level proficiency in leadership.

skills.name: Strategic Planning
skills.explanation: Developed and implemented business plans to increase revenue and growth, indicating strong proficiency in strategic planning.

skills.name: Marketing
skills.explanation: Utilized marketing strategies to increase patient referrals, showing a solid working proficiency in marketing.

skills.name: Project Management
skills.explanation: Introduced, negotiated, and implemented new projects to expand scope of engagement, suggesting strong proficiency in project management.

skills.name: Healthcare Management
skills.explanation: Extensive experience in healthcare management, including managing rehab departments and outpatient facilities, indicating expert-level mastery.

skills.name: Community/Volunteer Services
skills.explanation: Mentioned as an interest, but no relevant experience or skills demonstrated.
